start steps
1) go to firebase and sign inn your account
2) go to console and create project which you wanna deploy


setup firebase in local system
1)open terminal or cmd its uo to you which operating sysytem you are using
2)go to nodejs.org and install lts version of it.
3)now check npm node -v to ensure that u have correctly installed node in your system.
4)now install firebase in your local system by using "npm install firebase tool"
5)go to the project directory and open terminal there and run command "firebase login " to login your account
6)"firebase init" to initialize your project to firebase
7)select desire options
8)run command "firebase deploy"


